casebody.data:
Fourth Department,

September, 1936.

(September 23, 1936.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Ervin D. Lee, Property 1431 Genesee Street, Respondent, v. Frank J. Winslow and Others, Constituting the Board or Department of Assessment and Taxation of the City of Utica, New York, and Anthony Sisti, Clerk of the City of Utica, Appellants.

Order affirmed, with costs. All concur. (The order confirms report of referee reducing assessment on real property.) Present — Sears, P. J., Taylor, Thompson, Crosby and Lewis, JJ.
